OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dull and blustery day, with
OL,6,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, which could
OL,7,Fbe heavy at times. Gradually improving
OL,8,Ffrom the north with bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells possible later. Feeling milder
OL,10,Fdespite the cloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy into the
OL,13,Fevening, perhaps with a few blustery
OL,14,Fshowers before skies clear for a time
OL,15,Ffrom the north. Turning cloudier again
OL,16,Ffrom the west towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
